Part of Charles-Hubert's premium collection, the Charles-Hubert, Paris Stainless Steel Two-Tone Mechanical Pocket Watch 3553-T is a precision crafted timepiece with 17-jewel winding movement, skeletal display, and white dial with 24 hour sun and moon subdial. Elegant and contemporary, this watch arrives in a deluxe blue giftbox with matching curb chain.
